-- LDK Solar Says Liangbao Zhu Resigns From Board of Directors
-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 2013-03-18T10:23:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-18/ldk-solar-says-liangbao-zhu-resigns-from-board-of-directors.html
LDK Solar Co., the second-biggest
solar wafer maker said that Liangbao Zhu, a member of the board
of directors, resigned from the company effective yeterday.  Zhu, who had also served as executive vice president of the
Xinyu, China-based company, stepped down “for personal
reasons,” LDK said today in a PR Newswire statement.    To contact the reporter on this story:
